description:
Minimal taxonomy + minimal output columns.

How it works:
- categoryGroup selects the Explore section: business-needs / industries / products
- categoryPreset is the label(s) you want to run (Actor resolves real crawl targets from taxonomy.json)
- appGroup is optional override: if provided, it will crawl exactly these Explore filter values.

Demo (Business Needs): {"mode":"apps","categoryGroup":"business-needs","sphere":"business-needs","categoryPreset":["sales"],"maxPages":2,"headless":true}
Demo (Industries): {"mode":"apps","categoryGroup":"industries","sphere":"industries","categoryPreset":["automotive"],"maxPages":2,"headless":true}
Demo (Products): {"mode":"apps","categoryGroup":"products","sphere":"products","categoryPreset":["b2b-commerce"],"maxPages":2,"headless":true}
